label: British Library Add MS 15600 Decimus Junius Juvenal, Satires with scholia
description:
This manuscript contains the Satires (Satires) by the Roman poet Decimus Junius Juvenal (b. c. 50, d. after 127), together with marginal and interlinear glosses.
